snippet.title: Kitten'd - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit us on: https://www.kittend.com
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/842140/Kittend/
Oculus Store: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1549820201776682/
Viveport: https://www.viveport.com/apps/d629cafd-d770-4271-aeb4-a9b9e939a994/Kitten'd/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/KittendGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kittendgame/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kittendgame/

Kitten'd is a VR game where you are placed in a room filled with expensive breakable objects
and an overwhelming amount of cute kittens to take care of.

Feed them, clean them and keep them happy
 on 28 wacky levels and 4 different worlds.

Or just hang out with your virtual pets in the sandbox mode.
Earn points to buy cute hats or upgrade your home.
